sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant H as Handler Node
    participant P as Pigeon
    participant V as Validator
    participant B as Blockchain

    U->>H: Submit Message Request
    H->>B: Register Delivery Task
    B->>H: Issue Challenge Hash
    H->>P: Attach Message Payload
    
    Note over P: Physical Delivery Phase
    P->>P: Navigate to Destination
    
    P->>H: Complete Delivery
    H->>V: Submit Delivery Proof
    V->>B: Verify & Record Proof
    B->>H: Issue PGN Tokens
    B->>U: Confirm Delivery